canonical:
  title: 登極賀牋
  author: 李詹
  language: lzh
  text: 恭承內禪之美謳謌有歸蔚啓重光之休宗社永賴瞻聆所及蹈舞惟均恭惟性禀精明才兼勇智恪遵聖訓不煩師傅之勤斷决政機實致臣民之治爰當嘉會益膺純禧伏念任察農郊獲聞勝事謹詣趨蹌之列倍殫頌禱之誠
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 登極賀牋
  author: 李詹
  language: lzh
  text: 恭承內禪之美。謳謌有歸。蔚啓重光之休。宗社永賴。瞻聆所及。蹈舞惟均。恭惟性禀精明。才兼勇智。恪遵聖訓。不煩師傅之勤。斷决政機。實致臣民之治。爰當嘉會。益膺純禧。伏念任察農郊。獲聞勝事。謹詣趨蹌之列。倍殫頌禱之誠。
korean:
  title: 등극 하 전
  author: 이첨
  language: kor
  text: 공손히 내선(內禪)의 아름다운 명(命)을 받자와 만민(萬民)의 구가(謳歌)가 돌아갈 데가 있고, 울연(蔚然)히 중광(重光)의 복을 여기어 종사(宗社)가 길이 의뢰(依賴)하게 되었으니, 견문(見聞)이 미치는 곳마다 기뻐 춤춤이 모두 고르도소이다. 공손히 생각하옵건대, 타고나신 정명(精明)한 성품으로 용지(勇智)의 재주를 겸하시어 성훈(聖訓)을 각별히 준수하여 사부(師傅)의 부지런한 가르침을 번거로이 하지 않으시고 정치의 틀[政機]를 단호(斷乎)히 결정하여 실로 신민(臣民)의 지치(至治)를 이룩하셨사오니 이제 가회(嘉會)를 맞이하여 더욱 순복(純福)을 받자옵나이다. 엎드려 생각하옵건대, 농교(農郊)를 맡아 순찰(巡察)하옵다가 승사(勝事)를 얻어 듣자옵고, 삼가 추창의 반열(班列)에 나아가 곱절로 송도(頌禱)의 정성을 다하옵나이다.
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0350_010_0500&viewSync=OT
  footnotes: []
english:
  title: A Memorial for the Ascension
  author: Lee Cham
  language: eng
  text: |-
    How graciously we receive this noble mandate of inner abdication,
    and the songs of the people find their rightful home.
    Brilliant as the dawn of renewed light, our dynasty's fortune
    shines eternal, to be cherished through the ages.
    Wherever sight and hearing reach, all hearts leap in joy,
    and dancers move as one in celebration.

    With utmost reverence, I reflect upon your sage nature—
    born with clarity of mind and wisdom's keen insight.
    You honor the sacred teachings without need of tutors' labor,
    and govern with decisive will, bringing true order to realm and people.
    Now that this auspicious moment has arrived,
    may fortune's purest blessings attend you.

    In humble contemplation, while overseeing the rural fields,
    I have learned of these glorious affairs.
    With grateful steps I join the ranks of those who pay homage,
    pouring forth my deepest devotion in this song of praise.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: This is a congratulatory memorial (牋) composed upon the enthronement of a new ruler following the peaceful transfer of power through inner abdication, a valued practice in Confucian governance.
  - key: ''
    value: The phrase 'inner abdication' (內禪) refers to the formal abdication of a reigning monarch in favor of their successor, a ceremony considered the epitome of virtuous rulership in East Asian political philosophy.
